"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-uk-1936344-olympics-paris-2024-gold-medalist-horror-flight-secret\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A flight home for Olympic gold medalist Daniel Wiffen left members of the public horrified after a flight secret was inadvertently unveiled.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Irish athlete was seen posing wth his gold and bronze medals from this year's Olympics, held in Paris, alongside an Irish flag.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 148, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.7951893855934606, \"rank\": 0.24482698174156192, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998517524, \"rank\": 1.4803754527920785e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was not the pose or positioning of the flag which turned users onto a flight hack but where the photo was taken.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen, who picked up a gold medal in the Men's 800m Freestyle Swimming event, can be seen holding his pair of medals and dangling out the front of the plane - something members of the public did not think was possible.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One user wrote: \\\"I did not know those windows opened and now I have a new fear.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fair play to Daniel and all, I would have just been more comfortable not knowing you could slide back to cockpit windows like they are on an old Nissan Micra.\\\"\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan\", \"score\": 0.9999999968667908, \"rank\": 1.6905435464108736e-09, \"text\": \"Nissan\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan_Micra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Micra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan_Micra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nissan_Micra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Imane Khelif 'names Elon Musk and JK Rowling in lawsuit' after boxing gender row  Members of the public have since tried to calm the worried flyer and say it takes a little more than a roll up handle to open and close the cockpit windows.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One Twitter/X user replied: \\\"From memory it takes a bit of work to open them.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You'd sometimes see them open when plane parked for pilot to talk with ground crew.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing to fear nowadays.\\\"\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another reassured the original poster, adding: \\\"They are very hard to open on the Airbus so if you fly Aer Lingus you are fine.\\\"\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aer_Lingus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.38355707982878e-36, \"text\": \"Aer Lingus\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aer_Lingus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aer_Lingus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Olympic star Daniel Wiffen rushed to hospital after missing closing ceremony  Do not miss:Wiffen has big plans for final Olympics weekend after bagging Ireland two medals  Do not miss:NASCAR star explains belief he's superior driver to F1 champion Max Verstappen  But other users recalled an infamous incident where a pilot was sucked out the front of the plane window.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9995987225682589, \"rank\": 0.00040142024330257046, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"score\": 0.9999932854191558, \"rank\": 6.687308426915703e-06, \"text\": \"NASCAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 7.2